title: Wood Designs WD13803 See-All Storage with (12) Assorted Color Trays, 21 x 33 x 14" (H x W x D)
features: Three-level storage rack containing 12 assorted-color plastic storage trays, swivel casters
Preassembled plywood unit with eased edges and corners for safety and UV-resistant natural finish
21 x 33 x 14 inches (H x W x D)
UL Greenguard Gold certified for safety in educational environments
description: The Wood Designs WD13803 storage rack has three levels containing 12 assorted-color plastic storage trays for toys and supplies and rolls on casters for moving around a room. The rack measures 21 x 33 x 14 inches (H x W x D) and each tray measures 5 x 8 x 12 inches (H x W x D). (H is height, the vertical distance from lowest to highest point; W is width, the horizontal distance from left to right; D is depth, the horizontal distance from front to back.) The preassembled unit is made of plywood with eased edges and corners for safety and has an ultraviolet (UV)-resistant natural finish that also resists stains and damage from cleaning solutions. This storage rack is Underwriters Laboratories (UL) Greenguard Gold certified for environmental safety and is suitable for use in an educational environment.
Wood Designs manufactures children's furniture for educational environments. The company, founded in 1994, is headquartered in Monroe, NC.
